{
  "text": "The empirical analysis of the paper employs a slight modification of the [CITATION_1] HCEF that estimates the impact of different degrees on graduate earnings, after controlling for a standard set of demographic characteristics. The Mincer-type earnings functions that are fitted are defined as follows:",
